2. Max wallet 2%. 
3. Auto burn of tax accumulated in contracts to reduce contract dumps and increases price floor.

1,000,000 supply

TG: https://t.me/babycaspertoken
WEB: http://babycasper.io


This is a relaunch-but v1 holders took refunds in BNB or another tokens.
Already listed in CG/CMC and audited

